Class AirportWaypoint

java.lang.Object
org.jxmapviewer.beans.AbstractBean

planeair.components.mapview.mapwp.MapWaypoint
planeair.components.mapview.mapwp.airportwp.AirportWaypoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.jxmapviewer.viewer.Waypoint
Direct Known Subclasses:
ActiveAirportWaypoint, InactiveAirportWaypoint
public abstract class AirportWaypoint extends MapWaypoint
This class is the MapWaypoint which is used to represent Airports on the Map. The Airport class's Waypoints can be "active", in red, or "inactive", in gray. The active/inactive visual is made by children classes : ActiveAirportWaypoint and InactiveAirportWaypoint. AirportWaypoint extends MapWaypoint
